name: Esther
description:
I love mostly outdoors for fun, like i love reading, listening to music and clubbing,I love dirt bike riding, snowboarding, taking my boat to the lake, wake boarding and fishing and i also love visiting new places and lot more…. I am single and never married
I am not married for once , but i have been into a long time relationship which laid me into hard times and it hurts me so dearly and i don’t to be hurt by any man like that again.. I don’t have kids. I will love to have kids if i can find a very good and loving man of my dream . my best colour is Blue and i can also go with Yellow . I love vegetable and shrimp. I stay alone .
I don’t smoke and i dont drink socially
